Global Blockchain In Automotive Market Insights
Blockchain In Automotive Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 9.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 28.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Blockchain In Automotive Market Overview
The global blockchain in automotive market was valued at USD 0.35 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 2.84 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 33.8% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for secure and transparent transactions, the adoption of blockchain for vehicular identity management, and the rise of programmable blockchains for new services. Additionally, the integration of blockchain with connected cars and autonomous driving technologies is expected to further propel market expansion.

